(Next episode)

73
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:26,140
♪When I start to lose my confidence♪

74
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:28,140
♪Under the sunset♪

75
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,600
What can we do

76
